text: Barbora Balážová (born 18 March 1992 in Topoľčany)Profile at Sports- Reference.com is a Slovak table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's singles event, in which she was eliminated in the second round by Li Fen. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Slovakia Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2015 European Games Category:Table tennis players at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Slovakia Category:People from Topoľčany
